	<title>The effects of chronic illness on children of 0-3 years and their
   families.</title>

	<author>Himmelhoch-A.</author>

	<source>Australas-Nurses-J. 1977 Jun. 6(11). P 14-6.</source>

	<abstract>I have taken as examples of chronic illness in infancy four
   different types of disability: emotional deprivation, infants with
   sub-normal development, children suffering from mucodiscoidosis, and
   children who have neoplastic disease.</abstract>

